{
  "stem": "21004.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then he would give us, you know, let's say meat every week, five pounds of meat, or give us fruit or give us liquor, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You can-- I say, how can you give and I'll give you and I have to give this one, I have to give this one.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There's a lot of people to give in the city, the mayor, the-- the head from the-- from the restaurant.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So where I'm going to take to give?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He say, you go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'll tell you what to do and you'll be all right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We will go to the slaughter house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You'll bring him liquor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you give him liquor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You give him coffee.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You give him chocolate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He'll write it down 100 pounds of meat less than they slaughtered the cows.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody would know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He write it down so you can give us, you can give somebody else, and the rest you take for yourself and you can sell too.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's what they told me right in my eyes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You can sell to-- nobody lives in Russia without whatever we get from the government.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Russians were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no war going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was sit still, you know, and you have a job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the rest of Europe, oh, I tell you, we know that where the Germans are, they were for the Jews was very bad.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We know that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was very bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But for a while, there was no more wars, except Germany went further and further, took over Hungary and Romania and Estonia and so on and so on, you know.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in the meanwhile, he say, if you are going to give us, support us, we know when inspection comes from a city, let's say from Lemberg, to inspect your magazine.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
